---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Hey there and welcome to my site"
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2026')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		You probably got lost on the internet and found this page - my name is IR and welcome to my corner of the web. I'm thrilled to share a bit about who I am and what drives me in life.
	</p>

	<h2>Family First</h2>
	<p>
		My family is my greatest treasure and the foundation of everything I do. I am blessed with an amazing wife who stands by my side through every journey, and two beautiful daughters who fill my days with laughter, wonder, and purpose. Being a husband and father has taught me what true love really means - it's about sacrifice, patience, and showing up every single day for the people who matter most.
	</p>

	<p>
		Every moment with them - from morning coffee with my wife to playtime with my daughters - reminds me why I do what I do. Their smiles, their hugs, their dreams inspire me to be a better man. I practice love through being present, listening with my whole heart, and creating memories that will last a lifetime. My wife and daughters are my why, and I'm grateful every day for the privilege of loving them and being loved by them.
	</p>

	<h2>Health & Wellness</h2>
	<p>
		Sport and exercises are essential to my physical and emotional well-being. They keep me strong, focused, and grounded. Whether it's staying active or pushing my limits, I believe a healthy lifestyle complements a healthy mind and spirit - which helps me be the best version of myself for my family.
	</p>

	<h2>My Passions</h2>
	<p>
		The World Cup is currently playing, and soccer is my favorite sport! Beyond that, I'm an avid video gamer - these hobbies bring me joy and help me express my passion for life. I love the competition, the strategy, and the escape they provide after a long day. These aren't just pastimes; they're how I recharge and connect with my interests.
	</p>

	<p>
		Thanks for visiting and getting to know me a little better. This is just the beginning of the stories I want to share!
	</p>
</Layout>
